entries.femaleVariant: Guard up, you idiot!
Who's winning?
Hernandez! Ya know, in the old days that cripple Malone would've been flat on the boards!
Miss it, don't you.
Got cash ridin' on this?
Miss it?
You bet on this fight?
Go on, punch him!
Ah…
Nah. Just lookin'. Heh, it's outta habit more'n anything else.
Argh…
Jab with your left! Left, goddammit!
Now every last fighter's got extra skull lining… absorbs seventy-five percent of every blow.
How's it even possible? Seein' him?
Why'm I relivin' Johnny's memories?
You two share a brain now.
Tried to flatline me, Johnny did.
Hey, gotta run. See ya, Vick.
Drop by anytime.
What?!
What can I do suppress him? Y'know, avoid my murder?
Well... long as you don't give him control, can't do too much harm. 'Course that won't necessarily be possible after some time.
Well, that biochip is designed for users to communicate with constructs. It's just doin' its job.
He has access to your senses, perceptions, even some memories. Likewise, you've got a glimpse into his.
Got a few questions about Silverhand and this chip.
I'm no expert but fire away, see what I can do.
Let's talk Johnny and the chip.
Why am I seeing his memories?
See you later.
Have a good one.
Need to think on replacing my implants.
Was thinkin' about swappin' some chrome. Got any new toys?
Have a look.
Want to pay off my debt.
Finally scrounged up enough eddies to pay you back in full.
Hold onto 'em just in case - you need 'em more than me.
See ya 'round, V.
I'm not takin' 'em all the way to my grave, Vik. Here.
And thanks again for doing so much work on me 'thout ever seein' an enny.
That's what friends're for.
You... took care of Jackie's body?
I... I thought  you knew... Dammit, must've been knocked out when I talked about it...
W-whaddaya mean?
Arasaka... They swooped in, dug their claws into him.
What?! Where'd they take him?
Not sure. Had me face down to the ground, hands on my head. Tried to learn something but, well, you know how it is with corpos.
Fuckin' monos.
Did you take care of Jackie's body?
And what then?
Whaddaya say we don't let things get that far? Find a way to get rid of Silverhand, and fast.
So I got Arasaka to thank.
Y'know, I wager you have the lowest net worth of any Relic owner out there.
After a while, won't even know whose is whose.
What do I do if he tries to kill me?
Why can I see him?
Actually, gotta run.
How's biz?
How's biz going?
Eh, can't complain. Corpos learned to keep their distance. And Saka's back hiring lone mercs – they all gotta have the newest, shiniest implants.
Good thing you got Misty here to help. Handles your griping well.
Yeah, rentin' outta her shop's the best decision I ever made.
Know what? Seems like you're the only person in Night City who's happy with his lot.
You get to a certain age, you drop all your illusions. Life just gets easier from there.
Who's winning?
